109
00:53:35,697 --> 00:53:56,251
Bricks, mortar, infrastructure and the needs of public safety will always be central municipal concerns. But these concerns are addressed by real people. They are people who serve day in and day out. Many are with us today and I thank you for your dedication, the department heads of the City of Medford and those employees that are here today. Thank you.

110
