120
00:58:55,310 --> 00:59:24,335
I'm sure they really appreciate your support because I'm going to keep them really busy the next six months. And now I'd like to have the family members of the Medford City Council stand up and be recognized. Thank you. I plan to keep them busy too.

121
00:59:26,393 --> 00:59:44,078
