123
01:00:12,158 --> 01:00:27,920
This is good and pleases God, our Savior, who wants all people to be saved, to come to a knowledge of the truth. Let us bow our heads. Eternal God, our Heavenly Father, we pray for wisdom.

124
01:00:28,021 --> 01:00:44,727
for light, and for boundaries to protect our city, to protect our leaders, and to protect our families. We pray from the least of these to the greatest. May our city be open and welcome.

