131
01:03:18,610 --> 01:03:42,775
Corey Barrasso, the chef instructor of the Bistro 489, and Chad Fallon, the director of the Vocational Technical School for preparing the collation. And to all of you for coming out in the cold and braving it to be part of an important community event. At this time, I would ask the police honor guard to retire the colors.

132
01:04:29,738 --> 01:04:48,014
Please stand.

133
01:05:44,107 --> 01:06:00,357
